		<summary>
			<para>
       Gets a value indicating whether a property
       can be set only at design time.
    </para>
		</summary>
		<value>
			<para>
				<see langword="true "/>if a property 
       can be set only at design time; otherwise, <see langword="false"/>.
    </para>
		</value>
	</doc>
